window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>With his secret out, Miles’ life has changed irrevocably. He is the center of a wave from the media that he had not anticipated.</p> <p>Both good and bad, Miles must now navigate the political structure of Point City.</p> <p>Before Miles can be too content with his situation, he needs to remove the Brotherhood and the remnant of Roach’s organization.</p> <p>However, before he can mount an offense against Roach’s people, they make the first move. They don’t just come for him, but the entire Bureau of Superheroes.</p> <p>In the wake of the disaster, Miles must repair more than just his reputation.</p>"; 
